```yaml
        host: {{ .Values.serviceName }}
```

Change it to:
```yaml
        host: {{ include "epaylite-bridge-txn-service.fullname" . }}.{{ .Values.namespace }}.svc.cluster.local
```

That's the only edit needed. (This is already done in the file I gave you back — `isto-vs.yaml` in your outputs.)

